Oh, thank goodness you have come to!

probably more so than I think.

Why do you have a woman's hair

begins with them at the amusement park, the hottest place for couples in the area.

What is so fun about that?
Let us hurry up so we can ride it!

I will not worry about it.

I mean, this is supposed to be...

It is almost like a real date.

I will be done in a jiffy.

Yes, it looks perfect on you.

Oh, you were with that boy in the kimono earlier, right?

It would truly be a blessing... if we could be that close someday.

You used to be in love with a human.

Hey, what do you want to ride next?
You do not have to say anything if you do not want to!

How would he turn me away then?

Yes, it looks perfect on you.

I was almost jealous of the ferris wheel.
If Tomoe, like me, has decided
to live in the here and now, then I have found true happiness.
